com.igzcode.java.gae.util
Class ConfigUtil

java.lang.Object
  com.igzcode.java.gae.util.ConfigUtil

public class ConfigUtil
extends Object

Utility for save/get/delete configuration values easily. The values are readed from datastore and cached in memory. The configurations can be public or private.
